# Motion Rules

Use Framer Motion carefully.

## Allowed

- hover feedback
- tap feedback
- modal open / close
- dropdown open / close
- page transitions
- layout transitions
- loading-to-content transitions

## Avoid

- random decorative motion
- long animation chains
- motion that delays user action
- animation without state meaning

## Defaults

Use short transitions:

- duration: 0.15–0.35s
- ease: easeOut
- layout animations only when they improve continuity